	<datafield ind1="1" ind2="0" tag="245">
		<subfield code="6">880-03</subfield>
		<subfield code="a">Hādhā sharḥ al-faqīr ilá Rabbihi al-Ghanī Ibrāhīm ibn Aḥmad al-Mārghanī al-Tūnisī al-musammá (bi-Dalīl al-ḥayrān ʻalá Mawrid al-ẓamʼān) fī fannay al-rasm wa-al-ḍabṭ bi-iʻtibār qirāʼat al-Imām Nāfiʻ faqaṭ li-nāẓimihi al-shaykh al-imām al-ʻallāmah sayyidī Muḥammad ibn Muḥammad al-Sharīshī thumma al-Fāsī al-shahīr bi-al-Kharrāz, raḥimahu Allāh wa-raḍya ʻanhu, āmīn. Wa-yalīhi sharḥ laṭīf lil-shāriḥ al-madhkūr yusammá (Tanbīh al-Khullān ʻalá al-iʻlān bi-takmīl Mawrid al-ẓamʼān) fī rasm al-bāqī min qirāʼāt al-aʼimmah al-sabʻah al-aʻyān li-nāẓimihi al-imām al-fahhāmah al-shaykh sayyidī ʻAbd al-Wāḥid ibn ʻĀshir al-Andalusī, nafaʻanā Allāh bi-hi.</subfield>
